{
  "stem": "22979.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the sirens started, the SS running around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In no time, hundreds of SS men-- they brought in on-- on trucks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the sonderkommando, they were 600 boys, young boys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The sonderkommando, they always changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When new arrivals come, they gassed all the sonderkommando many times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And younger people, stronger, they-- they pushed into this kommando.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the sonderkommando started running.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Like I've mentioned, between our working place and the crematorium where the sonderkommando lived on top-- they lived in the same place where they worked-- tore through the-- broke through the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it was not voltage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And many of them were hiding in those piles of clothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we had to stay outside, all the Kanada unit, the working unit, worked there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And shivering and, you know, the screaming and yelling of the-- of the dogs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they went searching every barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "While they searched the barracks, naturally, they found in hiding two boys from the sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then the SS-- and it was Wunsch and Graf, which I mentioned, which I testified against them-- were dragging the two men by their hand and beating them out of the-- of the gate from where we were working and beating them and kicking them.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they killed them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And searching for the rest of the sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In the meantime, you know, it was fire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And it was really very, very scary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We knew now is the end of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Absolutely the end.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But what happened, you know, late in the day, they again found all the sonderkommando which was working there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They shot them all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They killed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And from this time, it was no more gassing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The [? blast-- ?] the sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
